NK037(ji)001:1: // dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i rnam rol zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)001:2: dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i rnam rol zhes bya ba /
NK037(ji)001:3: dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i bdag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:4: kun bzang he ru ka dpal gdul ka'i 'gror //
NK037(ji)001:5: rjes chags gtum drag gar gyis rnam rol pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:6: rdo rje srin po legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:7: he ru ka dpal de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:8: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rjes skyong phrin las bzhis //
NK037(ji)001:9: rnal 'byor re ba yongs skong bstan srung gtso //
NK037(ji)001:10: dgyes pa skyed byed phrin las cho ga'i khrigs //
NK037(ji)001:11: rgyud lung grub pa'i gzhung bzhin 'dir brjod bya //
NK037(ji)001:12: de la dang po dbang thob cing spyi dang bye brag gi dam tshigs la gnas pa'i sngags pas /
NK037(ji)001:13: don gnyis kyi bsam pa myur du 'grub pa'i las
NK037(ji)001:14: la basngagasa pa kho na'i dbang du byas nas thugs
NK037(ji)001:15: dam bskang zhing dam tshig gso ba'i phrin las kyi
NK037(ji)001:16: rim pa gtso bor sgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK037(ji)001:17: yo byad kyi bca' gzhi bya tshul dang /
NK037(ji)001:18: cho ga'i rim pa dngos las /
NK037(ji)001:20: nyi shu dgu la sogs pa'i dus gnyan khyad par
NK037(ji)001:21: can la sgrub khang ngam yid dang mthun pa'i gnas
NK037(ji)001:22: kyi steng logs rnams mdzes shing brjid pa'i spyan gzigs
NK037(ji)001:24: dam tshig gi bris sku sogs rten gyi mdun du
NK037(ji)001:25: rin po che'am thod pa la sogs pa'i snod du
NK037(ji)001:26: gtsang zhing bzang ba'i rgyu dam rdzas dang bcas pa
NK037(ji)001:27: la / dang por bla ma yi dam gyi gtor
NK037(ji)001:28: ma dpal bshos zlum brjid pad 'dab brgyad kyis bskor
NK037(ji)001:29: la / ba dang / nag po chen po'i gtor
NK037(ji)001:30: ma lcags mkhar kha bad can gyi steng du bshos
NK037(ji)001:31: bu gru gsum ha cang mi rno ba /
NK037(ji)001:32: de'i mdun du yum gyi bshos bu zur gsum pa dang /
NK037(ji)001:33: mkhar gyi rtsa ba'i mdun dang g.yas g.yon du 'khor
NK037(ji)001:34: gyi bshos bu gru gsum pa re dang rgyab tu
NK037(ji)001:36: de dag gi mtshams rnams su bshos phran chung ba brgyad dang /
NK037(ji)001:38: mda' bya rgod ma dar nag gyi cod pan can btsugs /
NK037(ji)001:39: sha khrag chang phud 'bru sman la du la phug
NK037(ji)001:40: 'khur ba chan sgog btsong sogs bza' bca' sna tshogs
NK037(ji)001:42: gzhan yang chos skyong ye shes pa'i rigs dang /
NK037(ji)001:43: 'jig rten pa gang brten rnams dang gzhi bdag gtor ma'i bar rim pa ma 'chol bar bsham /
NK037(ji)001:44: de dag gi g.yas su bdud rtsi /
NK037(ji)001:46: mdun du mchod yon sogs gtsang mar sbyar ba'i phyi'i mchod pa rnams dang /
NK037(ji)001:47: dbang po'i me tog sogs thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK037(ji)001:48: dam rdzas rnams dang 'brel ba'i mchod pa rnams phreng
NK037(ji)001:49: tshar du bkod / gzhan yang phyi nang gsang ba'i bskang rten mthun rdzas rnams dang /
NK037(ji)001:50: rdor dril nang mchod rnga sil rkang gling ha sti'i
NK037(ji)001:51: g.yab dar sogs dam rdzas kyi rnam grangs thams cad
NK037(ji)001:52: mthong brgyud kyi phyag len bzhin tshogs par bsham mo
NK037(ji)001:53: // gnyis pa cho ga'i rim pa dngos la bcu bdun las /
NK037(ji)001:54: dang po bdag gi rnam 'byor ni /
NK037(ji)001:55: spyir yi dam zhi khro gang la brten kyang rung mod /
NK037(ji)001:56: khyad par rgyud lung gi khro bo lta bu la byas na shin tu 'brel chags shing /
NK037(ji)001:57: gshin rje ltar sgrub pa sogs so so'i gnyen po'i lha ni de dang de'i skabs shes par bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:58: gnyis pa mchod rdzas rnams byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:59: bdag gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros ye
NK037(ji)001:60: shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas mchod rdzas kyi
NK037(ji)001:61: nyes skyon dngos 'dzin dri ma thams cad bsregs gtor
NK037(ji)001:63: stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang dur khrod drag po'i
NK037(ji)001:64: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab par a las b+hany+dza
NK037(ji)001:65: 'bar ba'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba rnams su
NK037(ji)001:66: h'u yig las byung ba'i mchod yon zhabs bsil me
NK037(ji)001:67: tog bdug spos snang gsal dri chab zhal zas rol
NK037(ji)001:68: mo la sogs pa phyi nang gsang ba'i 'dod pa'i
NK037(ji)001:69: yon tan so so'i mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su
NK037(ji)001:70: rdzogs pas nam mkha' rab 'byams gang ba rnams su
NK037(ji)001:72: de bzhin du shap+da'i bar sbyar ba lan gsum brjod cing rol mo'i sgras byin gyis brlab bo //
NK037(ji)001:73: sman phud ram yam kham gis bsang sbyang /
NK037(ji)001:74: stong pa'i ngang las a las byung ba'i thod pa'i
NK037(ji)001:75: nang du sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la h+aum t+r+aam
NK037(ji)001:76: h+r+aih+aah m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa
NK037(ji)001:77: zhu ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK037(ji)001:79: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)001:81: rak+ta yang de bzhin du bsang sbyang /
NK037(ji)001:82: stong pa'i ngang las a las byung ba'i thod pa'i
NK037(ji)001:83: snod du ram las nyi ma la gnas pa'i ram
NK037(ji)001:84: yig zhu ba las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho zhing gi lhu
NK037(ji)001:85: dum 'phyo ba'i rba klong 'khrugs pa la khams gsum
NK037(ji)001:86: gyi rak+ta thams cad bsdu shing thim par gyur /
NK037(ji)001:87: +aahh+aum ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+ai th+aa /
NK037(ji)001:90: stong pa'i ngang las rlung me thod pa'i sgyed pu
NK037(ji)001:91: gsum la gnas pa'i ye shes kyi ka p+aa la
NK037(ji)001:92: stong gsum dang mnyam pa'i nang du sha lnga bdud
NK037(ji)001:93: rtsi lnga sogs bza' bca' btung ba bldag gzhib 'dod
NK037(ji)001:94: yon lnga'i phung po zad mi shes pa'i logs spyod
NK037(ji)001:96: +aahh+aum ma h+aa ba ling+ta te dzo ba ling+ta ba
NK037(ji)001:97: la w+aa te gu h+ya sa ma ya h+aum h+r+aihth+aa
NK037(ji)001:98: / zhes lan bdun brjod pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK037(ji)001:99: gsum pa bla ma yi dam gyi gtor 'bul ni /
NK037(ji)001:100: rang gi snying ga'i sa bon las byung ba'i 'od
NK037(ji)001:101: zer gyis phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i bla ma rig 'dzin
NK037(ji)001:102: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams
NK037(ji)001:103: cad mkha' khyab kyi 'khor lor sad par bsam zhing
NK037(ji)001:105: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab cig dag pa'i sku //
NK037(ji)001:106: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK037(ji)001:107: thugs rje'i nga nga nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK037(ji)001:108: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:109: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aa na ma h+aa k+aa
NK037(ji)001:110: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK037(ji)001:112: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes pas spyan drangs /
NK037(ji)001:114: bla med mchog gi mchod la dam pa 'di //
NK037(ji)001:115: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK037(ji)001:116: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK037(ji)001:117: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:118: +aahmh'u gu ru man+dala de ba ga na sa pa
NK037(ji)001:119: ri w+aa re b+h+yaha r+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar yis phyi
NK037(ji)001:120: mchod dang / badz+ra pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:121: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:123: lha rnams kyi ljags h'u las byung ba'i rdo rje'i
NK037(ji)001:124: sbu gu can gyi 'od zer gyis gtor ma'i bcud
NK037(ji)001:125: drangs te gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK037(ji)001:126: i dam ba lim ta gri h+nan+tu ma ma sarba sid+d+hi m+me pra yats+tsha /
NK037(ji)001:127: zhes lan gsum gyi gtor ma phul la /
NK037(ji)001:129: gtum chen mas bstod cing phrin las gsol /
NK037(ji)001:130: mgron rnams 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim pas sdig sgrib thams cad sbyangs par bsam mo //
NK037(ji)001:131: bla ma yi dam gyi gtor 'bul so sor byed
NK037(ji)001:132: pa'i lugs kyang yod mod dbyer med du byed pa
NK037(ji)001:133: nyid gnas skabs su lag len zor yang zhing don
NK037(ji)001:134: la yang sngags kyi lam zhugs rnams kyis 'jig rten
NK037(ji)001:135: las 'das pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid bla ma'i ngo bor
NK037(ji)001:136: shes par bya'o // bzhi pa mdun bskyed gsal 'debs pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:137: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las bam 'phros te mdun du chad pa las /
NK037(ji)001:138: bam rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK037(ji)001:139: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug cing zhing chen gyi
NK037(ji)001:140: lang long 'phyo ba'i dbus su ri bo ma ya
NK037(ji)001:144: dug shing nags tshal stug pa'i ljongs /
NK037(ji)001:145: mi zad pa'i sprin gtibs shing /
NK037(ji)001:147: rgyob sod kyi 'brug sgra khol zhing /
NK037(ji)001:148: gnam lcags u rmo dang mtshon cha'i char 'bebs pa /
NK037(ji)001:149: khrag gi chu rgyun 'bab cing tshil bu'i 'brum chags pa /
NK037(ji)001:150: mi ro gsar rnying sna tshogs gcal du bkram zhing ro langs gar rtse ba /
NK037(ji)001:151: bya sha zan sna tshogs 'phur zhing lding ba //
NK037(ji)001:152: gcan gzan gtum po rnams ngar skad sgrog pas rgyug cing 'dril ba /
NK037(ji)001:153: rab tu 'jigs shing skyi g.ya' ba'i gnas su khrag
NK037(ji)001:154: dang sha chen rkang dang tshim bu klad pa dang
NK037(ji)001:155: lha ba rnag dang chu ser rnams kyis gang ba'i
NK037(ji)001:156: 'obs rim gyis yongs su bskor ba'i dbus su thugs
NK037(ji)001:158: b+h+r+aum bi shwa shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK037(ji)001:159: de yongs su gyur pa las dur khrod rol pa'i
NK037(ji)001:160: gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa rmangs bzhi
NK037(ji)001:161: lcags las byas pa'i steng du /
NK037(ji)001:165: byang bya'i thod pas brtsigs pa /
NK037(ji)001:166: srin po'i thod pa'i kha bad can /
NK037(ji)001:167: nyi zla gza' skar gyi 'od 'phro ba /
NK037(ji)001:170: rkang dang rtsib ma'i dral phyam /
NK037(ji)001:171: zhing lpags kyis thog phub pa'i rtser rdo rje'i tog gis mtshan pa /
NK037(ji)001:172: sgo bzhi lcags kyi sgo glegs dang rus pa'i rta babs kyis brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)001:176: glo snying gi 'phyang 'phrul sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan thams
NK037(ji)001:177: cad kyis brgyan pa'i nang khrag zhag 'khrug pa'i dbus
NK037(ji)001:178: su lcags mkhar nag po gru gsum lnga sgrom thod
NK037(ji)001:179: pa'i ra bas bskor ba'i gru gsum dbus ma'i nang
NK037(ji)001:180: du rdo rje phrag chen gtams pa'i gzhi la /
NK037(ji)001:181: pad+ma dang nyi ma'i steng du mi ro dang rta
NK037(ji)001:182: ro la gnas pa'i h+aum las gri gug h+aum gis
NK037(ji)001:183: mtshan par gyur / s+pha ra na phata /
NK037(ji)001:184: de las 'od zer 'phros pas dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad /
NK037(ji)001:186: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK037(ji)001:187: b+hu rkur ma h+aa k+aa la ya h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)001:188: dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po chen po rdo rje srin po'i gzugs can /
NK037(ji)001:189: sku mdog mthing nag thung zhing sbom la yan lag rags pa /
NK037(ji)001:190: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid can /
NK037(ji)001:191: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa'i gra nas khrag 'dzag pa /
NK037(ji)001:192: ljags 'dril zhing drag po'i rkan sgra sdeb pa /
NK037(ji)001:193: khro gnyer bsdus pa'i shangs nas 'thor byed kyi rlung sgra 'byin pa /
NK037(ji)001:194: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum sdang mig tu ldog pa /
NK037(ji)001:195: dbu skra dang sma ra smin ma kham nag gyen
NK037(ji)001:196: du 'bar ba las skar chen gyi 'od 'phro ba
NK037(ji)001:197: / phyag g.yas 'bar ba'i gri gug dang g.yon gdug
NK037(ji)001:198: pa can gyi khrag gis gang ba'i thod pa thugs
NK037(ji)001:200: mchan g.yas su tsan+dana gyi bing chen gzir ba'i bing stod nas lha dmag 'bum dang /
NK037(ji)001:201: bing smad nas bdud dmag nyi khri chig stong 'gyed pa /
NK037(ji)001:202: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber brtsegs mar gsol
NK037(ji)001:203: zhing gser sked nor bu'i mig tshangs can bcings pa
NK037(ji)001:204: / thod pa skam po lnga rigs lnga'i rtse bran can gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK037(ji)001:205: rlon pa khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu dang rdo rje'i do shal 'phyang ba /
NK037(ji)001:206: yan lag sbrul gyis dkris shing mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs sogs dur khrod 'jig pa'i chas can /
NK037(ji)001:207: sag t+wi'i lhwam yu ring gsol nas g.yon brkyang pa'i
NK037(ji)001:208: stabs kyis 'gying zhing brjid pas dgra bgegs rnams bardzisa
NK037(ji)001:209: pa / gtum zhing mi bsrun pa'i nyams can /
NK037(ji)001:210: spyi bor bya khyung nag po 'phur zhing lding ba /
NK037(ji)001:211: sta zur gnyis la seng ge ral pa sprugs pa /
NK037(ji)001:214: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na khams
NK037(ji)001:215: gsum dbang du sdud cing srid gsum zil gyis gnon
NK037(ji)001:216: pa'i bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)001:217: rak+sha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai rak+mo h'u /
NK037(ji)001:218: g.yon du nyi ma dang ro'i gdan la yum kro
NK037(ji)001:219: d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sku mdog sngon mo zhal gcig
NK037(ji)001:221: ral pa mthur du gtibs pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba /
NK037(ji)001:222: zhing gi pags pas stod g.yogs shing nyi zla gza' skar dang 'ja' 'od 'khrugs pa /
NK037(ji)001:223: stag lpags dang re lde'i smad dkris can /
NK037(ji)001:224: sbrul nag gi 'phyang 'phrul dang chu srin gyi thod pas brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)001:226: g.yon thod skyogs rus bcud rkang klad dang 'bru mar khrag chang gis gang ba rol zhing stob pa /
NK037(ji)001:227: g.yas su las kyi mgon po mdog nag cing mi sdug pa'i gzugs can /
NK037(ji)001:228: skra kham pa gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK037(ji)001:229: g.yas gri gug dang g.yon thod khrag thogs pa /
NK037(ji)001:230: g.yon brkyang gis ro'i gdan la bka' nod pa'i tshul gyis gnas pa'o //
NK037(ji)001:231: phyogs bzhi'i shar gyi lcags mkhar du pad nyi dgra
NK037(ji)001:232: bgegs kyi gdan la gnas pa'i h'u mthing nag las
NK037(ji)001:233: kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK037(ji)001:234: khro chen badz+ra king+ka ra sku mdog mthing nag rngams
NK037(ji)001:235: shing khros pa'i nyams can zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK037(ji)001:236: g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor zhing dmigs pa'i mgo
NK037(ji)001:237: lus 'dral ba / g.yon thod pa dgra bo'i snying khrag gis gang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK037(ji)001:238: mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs dang stag lpags kyi smad dkris can /
NK037(ji)001:239: sbrul dang thod pa'i brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)001:240: gri thogs ging chen bcu gnyis sogs las byed dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)001:241: lho'i lcags mkhar du dgra bgegs kyi gdan la ya dmar nag las /
NK037(ji)001:242: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK037(ji)001:243: gnod sbyin zangs mdog dmar nag kha gdangs shing rkan sgra sdebs pa /
NK037(ji)001:244: sdang mig gis dgra dpung sreg cing ral pa dmar po sprin ltar gtibs pa /
NK037(ji)001:245: g.yas gser gyi spu gri 'phyar zhing g.yon bswe mdung 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)001:246: yum bswe gdong zangs mgrin can dmar nag 'ja' tshon
NK037(ji)001:247: gyi gos can byad thag dang nad rkyal thogs pa
NK037(ji)001:250: mi dmar bshan pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sogs las byed dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)001:251: nub kyi lcags mkhar du pad nyi dgra bgegs kyi
NK037(ji)001:252: gdan la dza dmar nag las rak+sha dz+wa la sa
NK037(ji)001:253: ma ya / gza' bdud chen po r+aa hu la
NK037(ji)001:254: sku mdog dud kha srin po'i gzugs can mgo bo
NK037(ji)001:255: ma ya / dgu pa / lus kun mig gis gang zhing gtum rngams 'khrugs pa'i nyams can /
NK037(ji)001:256: g.yas gri gug 'phyar ba'i rtse las skyin thang gi
NK037(ji)001:257: 'khor lo bskor zhing g.yon thod khrag rngub cing chu
NK037(ji)001:260: zhing gi g.yang gzhi dang thod sbrul gyi phreng ba sogs 'jigs pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)001:263: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad sogs srid gsum dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)001:264: byang gi lcags mkhar du ma mthing nag las tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK037(ji)001:265: 'dod khams bdag mo re ma t+ai nag mo skem zhing rid la gtum pa'i nyams can /
NK037(ji)001:266: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa'i bar du mi ro rengs po gsol ba /
NK037(ji)001:267: drag po'i rkan sgra sdeb cing shangs nas nad kyi na bun 'thul ba /
NK037(ji)001:268: lte ba nas nyi ma 'char zhing /
NK037(ji)001:269: spyi bor zla ba tshes pa /
NK037(ji)001:270: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang thod rlon gyi do shal can /
NK037(ji)001:271: snyan g.yas la seng ge dang g.yon pa sbrul dang dril bus brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)001:273: g.yon nad rkyal dgra la 'gyed pa /
NK037(ji)001:274: mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs dang re lde'i smad dkris
NK037(ji)001:275: sbrul gyi ske rags can drel rta rkang gsum srin
NK037(ji)001:276: po'i thod pa'i sga dang sbrul gyi gong smed can
NK037(ji)001:277: la chibs nas rak+ta'i rgya mtshor rol pa /
NK037(ji)001:281: bdud kyi khram bam ste sprul pa'i mtshon cha lnga 'chang ba /
NK037(ji)001:282: nag mo 'bum sde'i 'khor dang bcas te rlung nag 'tshub ma'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)001:283: de'i phyi rol btson khang bcu drug la goo r+ai ma sogs ma mo chen mo brgyad dang /
NK037(ji)001:284: sid+ha ma sogs phra men ma brgyad /
NK037(ji)001:285: khyams kyi khor yug la dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK037(ji)001:286: gra bzhir skem ma sogs gru 'debs ma bzhi /
NK037(ji)001:287: sgo bzhir brtson mo sogs sgo srung bzhi /
NK037(ji)001:288: gzhan yang slas dang byi mo bran mo ru 'dren
NK037(ji)001:289: gyi pho nya sogs ci bgyi'i bka' nyan 'khor tshogs
NK037(ji)001:290: bsam gyis mi khyab pas bskor ba /
NK037(ji)001:291: phyi'i 'obs mkhar rnams na 'bu dang 'bu chen sbrang ma dang sbrang rgod bung ba dang dug sbrul /
NK037(ji)001:292: sdom dang sdig pa la sogs pa dgra bo'i sha rus g.yeng zhing rol pa /
NK037(ji)001:294: khra rgod khwa ta sogs bya sha zan mang po 'phur zhing lding bas nam mkha' gang ba /
NK037(ji)001:295: lce spyang dang seng ge stag gzig dom dred 'phar
NK037(ji)001:296: ba la sogs pa gdug pa'i gcan gzan sna tshogs
NK037(ji)001:297: ngar skad dang bcas pas sha za zhing lang long
NK037(ji)001:298: du 'phyo bas sa gzhi khyab pa /
NK037(ji)001:299: gzhan yang sprul pa dang yang sprul pho nya las
NK037(ji)001:300: byed sde brgyad dregs pa'i dmag tshogs bsam gyis mi
NK037(ji)001:301: khyab pa'i tshogs thams cad kyang phrin las 'dod dgur
NK037(ji)001:302: bsgyur zhing sgrub pa po'i re ba skong bas nam
NK037(ji)001:303: mkha' bar snang sa gzhi thams cad yongs su gang
NK037(ji)001:304: bar bsam mo // gtso bo zhal gsum phyag drug
NK037(ji)001:305: bsgom par 'dod na rgyud kyi le'u bco lnga pa
NK037(ji)001:306: las 'byung ba bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:308: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK037(ji)001:311: h+aum las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)001:312: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas mchog /
NK037(ji)001:313: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK037(ji)001:314: ma la ya gnam lcags 'bar ba'i ri bo /
NK037(ji)001:315: dur khrod chen po brgyad sogs rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK037(ji)001:316: nas dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po 'khor
NK037(ji)001:317: dang bcas pa thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar sprin
NK037(ji)001:318: phung gtibs pa bzhin byon par bsam la /
NK037(ji)001:319: lag pa'i mkhrig ma bsnol mathe'u chung gnyis spel mdzub mo lcags kyu ltar byas la /
NK037(ji)001:320: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)001:321: b+hu ra kur ma h+aa k+aa la ya sa ma
NK037(ji)001:322: ya hrim hrim am ku sha dzahdzah zhes brjod cing
NK037(ji)001:323: rkang gling gis drangs pa'i rol mo dang /
NK037(ji)001:326: dbyangs kyi 'gyur ba dang bcas pas /
NK037(ji)001:328: lang+ka yul yi grong brdal gyi //
NK037(ji)001:329: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK037(ji)001:330: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK037(ji)001:331: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK037(ji)001:332: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK037(ji)001:333: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas kyang //
NK037(ji)001:334: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK037(ji)001:335: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa //
NK037(ji)001:336: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:337: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK037(ji)001:338: nye gnas kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma //
NK037(ji)001:339: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK037(ji)001:340: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs dang //
NK037(ji)001:341: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:343: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK037(ji)001:344: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:346: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na
NK037(ji)001:347: ba ti sa p+aa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa k+aa
NK037(ji)001:348: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK037(ji)001:349: / +aa kar+sha ya h+aum dzah e a ral+li hrim hrim dzah dzah zhes pas spyan drang ngo //
NK037(ji)001:350: skabs 'dir zhal du rngub pa sogs khyad par gyi
NK037(ji)001:351: cho ga bshad pa ni bsnyen sgrub thun mong ma
NK037(ji)001:352: yin pa'i skabs kho nar dgongs pa'o //
NK037(ji)001:353: drug pa bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:355: rdo rje brag chen gtams pa dang //
NK037(ji)001:356: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen khri //
NK037(ji)001:357: bam chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK037(ji)001:358: rab 'jigs dpa' bo 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:360: bka' dang bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:361: bdun 'dul dbang phyug ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:362: srin yul lang+ka pu ri yi //
NK037(ji)001:363: grong khyer gtan nas brlag mdzad cing //
NK037(ji)001:364: lha ma yin gyi bu mo ni //
NK037(ji)001:365: glog sprin 'dul bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:366: lha chen mgon po nag po khyod //
NK037(ji)001:368: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)001:369: khas blangs dam bca' ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)001:371: phrin las mdzad phyir bzhugs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:372: b+h+aur kur ma h+aa k+aa la pad+ma kro d+h+r+ai shwa
NK037(ji)001:373: r+ai nag mo ting lam sa ma ya s+t+wam tish+tha
NK037(ji)001:375: bdun pa dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:376: dam tshig gi rgya bcings te rdo rje spyi bor bzhag /
NK037(ji)001:377: bdud rtsi ljags la byin par mos la /
NK037(ji)001:378: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)001:379: badz+ra sa ma ya ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)001:380: dpal rdo rje nag po chen po legs ldan tshogs
NK037(ji)001:381: kyi bdag po lcam dral 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK037(ji)001:382: kyis / kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen /
NK037(ji)001:383: rgyal tshab ston pa rigs lnga /
NK037(ji)001:384: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje /
NK037(ji)001:385: skal ldan rgyal po dzah slob dpon s+thi ra ma ti /
NK037(ji)001:387: bal po ba su d+ha ra /
NK037(ji)001:388: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK037(ji)001:392: bde gshegs zur mes dbon gsum nas nye bar bzung
NK037(ji)001:393: ste drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar du byon
NK037(ji)001:394: pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam
NK037(ji)001:395: las ma 'da' bar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs
NK037(ji)001:396: sogs kyis dam tshig gi gnyer gtad cing /
NK037(ji)001:399: sngon tshe dpal chen khro bo'i rgyal //
NK037(ji)001:400: bdud 'dul rdo rje srin po yis //
NK037(ji)001:401: dregs pa bcom nas sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK037(ji)001:402: dbang bskur ming btags srog snying phul //
NK037(ji)001:403: cho 'brang kun la dam tshig sbyin //
NK037(ji)001:404: bstan pa yongs su bsrung bar byas //
NK037(ji)001:405: phyi yi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)001:406: dpal mgon legs ldan nag po che //
NK037(ji)001:407: nang gi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)001:408: bdud 'dul dur khrod sgrol ba'i ging //
NK037(ji)001:409: gsang ba'i mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)001:410: sgrol byed rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK037(ji)001:411: mna' bor khas blangs ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)001:412: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:413: sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyar ba'i //
NK037(ji)001:415: dpal mgon dregs pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK037(ji)001:416: rtag tu dam tshig tshul bzhin gyis //
NK037(ji)001:418: badz+ra a mri ta ya hi sarba sa ma ya h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK037(ji)001:419: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK037(ji)001:420: zhes dam tshig gsos btab la bdud rtsi 'thor zhing bdag gis kyang myang ngo //
NK037(ji)001:423: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul bzlog cing //
NK037(ji)001:424: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:425: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)001:426: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK037(ji)001:427: bsod nams gzi brjid 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:428: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:429: spyod pa rlabs chen 'phags la drag shul mthu chen
NK037(ji)001:430: ldan la pha rol phyin bcu mnga' la sgrib pa
NK037(ji)001:431: rnam gnyis dag la bdag med gnyis rtogs khyod la
NK037(ji)001:432: ston pa'i lung bstan thob la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:433: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams dang dgongs pa gcig /
NK037(ji)001:434: rig 'dzin grub thob rnams dang byin rlabs gcig /
NK037(ji)001:435: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams dang dam tshig gcig /
NK037(ji)001:436: lha srin sde brgyad rnams dang mthu rtsal gcig /
NK037(ji)001:437: sngon gyi drang srong rnams dang smon lam gcig /
NK037(ji)001:438: tshogs bdag khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:439: mgon po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)001:440: a ti pu hoh bra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes phyag bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:441: dgu pa mchod pa 'bul ba la spyi dang khyad par gnyis las dang po ni /
NK037(ji)001:442: stong gsum 'di 'am stong gsum gzhan dag na //
NK037(ji)001:443: me tog phreng ba la sogs rin chen dbyig /
NK037(ji)001:444: la du la phug la sogs yid bzhin zas //
NK037(ji)001:445: thang skyes chu skyes la sogs longs spyod rkyen //
NK037(ji)001:446: 'chi med bdud rtsi la sogs dam tshig chu //
NK037(ji)001:447: gu gul tshil chen la sogs bdug pa'i sprin //
NK037(ji)001:448: zhun chen mar me la sogs snang gsal mchog /
NK037(ji)001:449: bshos gtsang bza' btung longs spyod sna tshogs pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:450: rim gsum mchod pa'i tshogs bdag mnyes gyur cig /
NK037(ji)001:451: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na pa ti sa
NK037(ji)001:452: pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra push+pe d+hu pe +aa lo
NK037(ji)001:453: ke gan+d+he nee wi d+ya shap+da pu dza hoh badz+rar+au
NK037(ji)001:454: pa shap+da gan+d+he r+aa sa spar+she p+au dza +aahh+aum /
NK037(ji)001:456: gnyis pa khyad par gyi mchod pa la bzhi las bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:458: lcang lo can gyi ma h+aa b+hany+dza ru //
NK037(ji)001:459: byang chub sems dang ma h+aa rak+ta dang //
NK037(ji)001:460: dri chen dri chu sha chen rnam pa lnga //
NK037(ji)001:461: gnyis med sbyar ba'i pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK037(ji)001:462: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK037(ji)001:463: mchod bzhes dam skongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)001:464: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:467: lung dang man ngag shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:468: nges pa'i lung ston dus gsum bla ma la //
NK037(ji)001:469: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK037(ji)001:470: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)001:471: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:472: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal ldan he ru ka /
NK037(ji)001:473: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lha tshogs la //
NK037(ji)001:474: rnam dag thugs rjes sarba pany+tsa rnal 'byor bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:475: dpal ldan mgon po yab yum 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)001:476: rnam dag thugs rjes sarba ging dang gnod sbyin srin po ma mo dang //
NK037(ji)001:477: bka' sdod las byed dregs pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK037(ji)001:478: rnam dag thugs rjes sarba zhes mtheb srin nyi zla'i gwa'usa lha so sor rkang 'thon du 'bul lo //
NK037(ji)001:481: ma h+aa rak+ta dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i khrag /
NK037(ji)001:482: m+au la rak+ta rang byung pad+ma'i khrag /
NK037(ji)001:483: chu dang ma 'dres dwangs ma'i khrag gi mtsho //
NK037(ji)001:484: zhing chen zhing chung rba klong 'khrug pa 'di //
NK037(ji)001:485: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK037(ji)001:486: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:489: snod kyi 'jig rten yangs pa'i gtor gzhong du //
NK037(ji)001:490: bcud kyi sems can thams cad gtor mar sbyar //
NK037(ji)001:491: lcags kyu lnga dang sgron ma'i dam tshig rdzas //
NK037(ji)001:492: ris su ma chad bza' btung longs spyod tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:493: legs ldan nag po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK037(ji)001:494: dam tshig bzhin du bzhes nas phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:495: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:497: mgon po yab yum 'khor bcas kyi ljags rdo rje'i
NK037(ji)001:498: sbu gu can gyis gtor ma'i bdud rtsi'i bcud drangs
NK037(ji)001:499: shing gsol bas tshim zhing dgyes par bsam la gtso
NK037(ji)001:501: i dam ba lim ta grih+na kha kha kh+aa hi
NK037(ji)001:502: kh+aa hi b+huny+dza ho rak+ta pi pa to sa ma
NK037(ji)001:503: ya s+w+aa h+aa / zhes lan bdun gyis phul ba'i mthar /
NK037(ji)001:504: dpal ma h+aa k+aa la khrag 'thung gi rgyal po /
NK037(ji)001:505: gtsug lag khang dang dkyil 'khor gyi srung ma /
NK037(ji)001:506: dug gsum nad kyi smad pa /
NK037(ji)001:508: bdud dpung sgrol ba'i dpa' bo /
NK037(ji)001:509: bstan pa'i bka' srung chen po /
NK037(ji)001:510: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po /
NK037(ji)001:511: yum chen kro d+h+ai shwa ri /
NK037(ji)001:513: gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal po /
NK037(ji)001:514: srin po gza' bdud chen po /
NK037(ji)001:517: pho nya las byed sha za bshan pa sogs 'dus
NK037(ji)001:518: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pho mo 'khor dang bcas
NK037(ji)001:519: pa rnams kyis mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen
NK037(ji)001:520: po 'di bzhes la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs
NK037(ji)001:521: sogs kyis gtor ma phul la phrin las bcol /
NK037(ji)001:522: khyad par gyi mchod pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:523: gtor ma la rak+ta bran te /
NK037(ji)001:524: rang gi thugs ka nas tsha zhing rtsub pa'i 'od
NK037(ji)001:525: zer 'phros pas mgon po 'khor bcas kyi rgyud bskul
NK037(ji)001:526: / sprul pa'i pho nya rnams kyis zhing bcur gyur
NK037(ji)001:527: pa'i dgra bgegs thams cad gtor ma la bstim par
NK037(ji)001:528: / bsam la / bden stobs brjod de dgug bstim bya /
NK037(ji)001:529: +aahh+aum gis sha khrag 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du spel la /
NK037(ji)001:531: rnal 'byor kun gyi dpal mgon mchog /
NK037(ji)001:532: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu rtsal can //
NK037(ji)001:533: dka' thub nag po tshur gson cig /
NK037(ji)001:534: legs ldan nag po ma rungs pa //
NK037(ji)001:535: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:536: rang gi rgyal srid la gnas te //
NK037(ji)001:537: gzhan gyi sde rnams pham mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)001:538: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK037(ji)001:539: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig gtso //
NK037(ji)001:540: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab /
NK037(ji)001:541: bswe byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK037(ji)001:542: ma dang sring mo chung ma la //
NK037(ji)001:543: dpa' bo khyod kyi rol par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:544: dam tshig chen pos ma btang zhig /
NK037(ji)001:545: zhe sdang can gyi bdag po rnams //
NK037(ji)001:546: sems can kun gyi srog 'phrog pa //
NK037(ji)001:547: dgra bo nyams pa'i srog dang phrol //
NK037(ji)001:548: sha dang khrag la longs spyod gyis //
NK037(ji)001:549: gnod sbyin chen po ma rungs rnams //
NK037(ji)001:550: bswe byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK037(ji)001:551: gser dngul dbyig nor kun longs la //
NK037(ji)001:552: rang gi 'dod pa'i longs spyod gyis //
NK037(ji)001:553: sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor bdag nyid la //
NK037(ji)001:554: yid bzhin nor bu'i dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)001:555: rigs ngan dme sha can gyi tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:556: ba lang khyi sha rta sha dang //
NK037(ji)001:557: mi sha glang chen sha sogs bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:558: sring mo khrag 'thung ma mo rnams //
NK037(ji)001:559: bsad pa'i khrag ni drod mo dang //
NK037(ji)001:560: bzhes shig dgra bo'i khrag la 'thungs //
NK037(ji)001:561: sprul pa'i phra men ma mo rnams //
NK037(ji)001:562: thod rus rkang dang 'bru mar dang //
NK037(ji)001:563: rdzu 'phrul grub pa'i dam rdzas bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:564: rigs ngan gdug pa'i bu mo rnams //
NK037(ji)001:565: sha chen gshang gci khu ba khrag /
NK037(ji)001:567: bdag gi nad rnams bzlog tu gsol //
NK037(ji)001:568: dmigs pa'i dgra la rims nad thongs //
NK037(ji)001:569: srid pa'i bud med ma rung rnams //
NK037(ji)001:570: bro gar glu tshig mchod pa bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:571: dmigs bya 'jo tshul stobs kyis phrogs //
NK037(ji)001:572: shor ba gzhon nu bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:573: rnal 'byor chen po'i bka' byung gis //
NK037(ji)001:574: sngags sgra drag po'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:575: dgra bo'i phung po rdul du rlog /
NK037(ji)001:576: log sred can gyi tshogs rnams nyon //
NK037(ji)001:577: yang dag gsang du kun rig na //
NK037(ji)001:578: che chung las gnyis gang byas kyang //
NK037(ji)001:579: gnyis ka'i dbang du mi 'gyur gyis //
NK037(ji)001:581: gsang tshig brten pa'i tshogs rnams nyon //
NK037(ji)001:582: gshang gci khrag dang sol khu yis //
NK037(ji)001:583: brgya 'am stong du bgos nas ni //
NK037(ji)001:585: dam rdzas mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:586: bcol ba'i las rnam sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:588: mnga' bdag chen po ma rungs pa //
NK037(ji)001:589: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa ste //
NK037(ji)001:590: khro bo'i rgyal po ging chen po //
NK037(ji)001:591: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhengs //
NK037(ji)001:593: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK037(ji)001:594: khas blang dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK037(ji)001:595: dam bca' tha tshig ma 'da' zhig /
NK037(ji)001:596: sngon du rig 'dzin gong mas bsgrubs //
NK037(ji)001:597: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bsgrub kyi //
NK037(ji)001:598: so so'i mos pa tha dad pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:599: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)001:600: ji ltar bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:601: ces gtso 'khor thams cad kyi sngags mthar /
NK037(ji)001:602: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:604: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:605: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:607: ma h+aa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:611: nee wi d+ya ba lim ta pi pa to ho zhes rkang 'thon du mchod par bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:612: bcu pa bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:614: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:615: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:616: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging //
NK037(ji)001:617: khro bo'i rgyal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)001:619: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:620: srin yul pu ri nag po'i dkyil //
NK037(ji)001:621: lang+ka yul gyi grong brdal na //
NK037(ji)001:622: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK037(ji)001:623: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK037(ji)001:624: drag shul byan lag ljongs kyi ri //
NK037(ji)001:625: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK037(ji)001:626: chos 'dzin rigs kyi sgrub gnas te //
NK037(ji)001:627: rdo rje thabs kyi lta ba'i yul //
NK037(ji)001:628: dug shing nags tshal stug po'i tshal //
NK037(ji)001:629: gnam lcags u rmo char bzhin 'bab //
NK037(ji)001:630: gsur chen dud pa sprin ltar gtibs //
NK037(ji)001:631: rnag khrag chu ser mtsho ru bskyil //
NK037(ji)001:632: sha rus phung po ri ltar spungs //
NK037(ji)001:634: bya gcan mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK037(ji)001:636: rab tu 'jigs pa'i gnas mchog na //
NK037(ji)001:637: drag po'i sku mkhar ldems se ldem //
NK037(ji)001:638: shar phyogs bam ri stag thod mkhar //
NK037(ji)001:639: stag thod 'dzum mdangs mu lu lu //
NK037(ji)001:640: lho phyogs bam ri mi thod brtsigs //
NK037(ji)001:641: mi thod spyugs pa tse re re //
NK037(ji)001:642: nub phyogs bam ri rta thod brtsigs //
NK037(ji)001:643: rta thod mtsher sgra lhangs se lhang //
NK037(ji)001:644: byang phyogs bam ri bya thod brtsigs //
NK037(ji)001:645: bya thod tsheg sgra di ri ri //
NK037(ji)001:646: srin po'i thod pa'i kha bad can //
NK037(ji)001:648: ngos la nga rgyal glog dmar khyug /
NK037(ji)001:649: rtse la dur bya nag po lding //
NK037(ji)001:650: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK037(ji)001:651: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i sgo mo gsal //
NK037(ji)001:652: 'jigs pa'i sku mkhar nang shed na //
NK037(ji)001:653: rta ro mang po gcal du bkram //
NK037(ji)001:654: mi ro mang po khri ru brtsigs //
NK037(ji)001:655: mi ro rta ro'i gdan steng na //
NK037(ji)001:657: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhugs //
NK037(ji)001:658: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK037(ji)001:659: phrin las drag po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK037(ji)001:660: khyad par mchog gi sku byung ba //
NK037(ji)001:661: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:662: tshogs bdag mgon por btags pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:663: dregs pa'i gtso bo mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:664: bar snang khams na bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:665: rdo rje'i gshog pa'i stobs ldan rtags //
NK037(ji)001:666: bcom ldan rdo rje sesama dpa' yis //
NK037(ji)001:667: lag tu rdo rje gtad pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:668: sngon byung dge slong thub dka' dang //
NK037(ji)001:669: thugs rje'i thabs kyis 'brel ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:670: ma h+aa k+aa lar btags pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:671: khas blangs don las mi 'gyur rtags //
NK037(ji)001:672: legs ldan nag por btags pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:673: rnal 'byor pho nya mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:674: mngags byed chen por btags pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:675: bcol ba'i las rnams mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:676: lang+ka'i yul na bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:677: lha srin bran du 'khol ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:678: ma la ya ru bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:679: drag shul stobs dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:680: thang dmar rgya mtshor bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:681: klu rnams dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:682: bsnyen pa'i tshul gyis bka' sdod pa //
NK037(ji)001:683: gang gsol las rnams g.yel med rtags //
NK037(ji)001:684: rdo rje'i brag la bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:685: 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos rtags //
NK037(ji)001:686: mi ro'i gdan la bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:687: ma tshogs dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:688: mthing nag ber chen gsol ba ni //
NK037(ji)001:689: rnal 'byor bu bzhin skyong ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:690: rdo rje'i phreng bas brgyan pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:691: las byed rdo rjer dbang bskur rtags //
NK037(ji)001:692: tsan+dana dbyug pa bsnams pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:693: khams gsum rdul du rlog pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:694: mtshon cha gri gug bsnams pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:695: sdang byed dgra srog gcod pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:696: thod rlon dmar chen bsnams pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:697: dam nyams snying khrag 'thung ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:698: mthing nag khro gtum rngams pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:699: mngon spyod drag po'i las mdzad rtags //
NK037(ji)001:700: sbyor yum sku la 'khril ba ni //
NK037(ji)001:701: thabs shes zung 'jug brnyes pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:702: zhabs la stag mo 'khyug pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:703: gnod sbyin las la 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:705: za byed pho nyar 'gyed pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:706: sta zur seng chen rngams pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:707: ging tshogs pho nyar 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:708: dbu la khyung gis brgyan pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:709: gza' gdong pho nyar 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)001:710: gdug pa'i rgyan rnams ldan pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:711: rdzu 'phrul dpag yas ngo mtshar rtags //
NK037(ji)001:712: bdud 'dul dbang phyug nag po che //
NK037(ji)001:713: dam tshig can la bdag bstod do //
NK037(ji)001:714: rtse gcig sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod la //
NK037(ji)001:715: pha ltar skyob cing bu ltar 'grogs //
NK037(ji)001:716: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar dungs //
NK037(ji)001:717: ma g.yel bcol ba'i las mdzad phyir //
NK037(ji)001:718: mi mngon dbyings nas sku bzhengs la //
NK037(ji)001:719: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK037(ji)001:720: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:722: g.yon gyi phyogs nas sku byung ba //
NK037(ji)001:723: nye gnas kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma //
NK037(ji)001:724: gtum po'i srin mo 'jigs tshul can //
NK037(ji)001:725: zhal gcig phyag gnyis thal ba'i mdog /
NK037(ji)001:726: khrag ral dmar po mun ltar gtibs //
NK037(ji)001:727: ral pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro //
NK037(ji)001:728: sku stod zhing chen g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK037(ji)001:730: sku smad stag lpags re lde la //
NK037(ji)001:731: sbrul nag chu srin thod pas brgyan //
NK037(ji)001:732: g.yas pa sbrul zhag yab la 'khyud //
NK037(ji)001:733: g.yon pa thod skyogs khrag gis bkang //
NK037(ji)001:734: rus bcud rkang mar klad pa la //
NK037(ji)001:735: 'bru mar chang dang sbyar ba dag /
NK037(ji)001:736: rtag par rang gis longs spyod cing //
NK037(ji)001:737: yab la stob cing dgra la 'phen //
NK037(ji)001:738: 'jigs pa'i ma mo khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)001:739: sngon gyi dam bca' ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)001:740: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:742: shar phyogs thod mkhar 'jigs pa na //
NK037(ji)001:743: khro bo'i rgyal po king ka ra //
NK037(ji)001:744: sku dmog mthing nag 'jigs tshul can //
NK037(ji)001:745: phyag g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK037(ji)001:746: g.yon pa thod rlon snying khrag 'thung //
NK037(ji)001:747: gri thogs ging chen 'khor gyis bskor //
NK037(ji)001:748: gsang ba'i bdag pos dbang bskur nas //
NK037(ji)001:749: rdo rje chos zhes ming btags pa //
NK037(ji)001:750: mthu stobs rtsal ldan khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)001:751: bcol pa'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:753: lho phyogs bswe sdong lcags mkhar na //
NK037(ji)001:754: yab gcig gnod sbyin zangs mdog ni //
NK037(ji)001:755: sku mdog dmar nag brjid pa la //
NK037(ji)001:756: dbu la rgya mdud 'khor lo brtsegs //
NK037(ji)001:757: ral pa dmar po sprin ltar gtibs //
NK037(ji)001:758: spyan dmar dam nyams dgra la ldog /
NK037(ji)001:759: 'jigs pa'i zhal ni bsgrad pa la //
NK037(ji)001:760: mche ba gnam lcags dgu khris gtams //
NK037(ji)001:761: sku la shun gyi g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK037(ji)001:762: g.yas pa gser gyi ral gri 'phyar //
NK037(ji)001:763: g.yon pa bse mdung dmar po bsnams //
NK037(ji)001:764: ba dan dmar po glog ltar 'khyug /
NK037(ji)001:765: 'jigs su rung dang dpa' byad can //
NK037(ji)001:766: yum chen bse gdong zangs mgrin can //
NK037(ji)001:767: bka' nyan gyad chen lha srin brgyad //
NK037(ji)001:768: bse mo ging chen las la 'gyed //
NK037(ji)001:769: gtum chen dregs pa'i tshogs la bstod //
NK037(ji)001:770: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:772: nub phyogs drag po'i lcags mkhar na //
NK037(ji)001:773: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK037(ji)001:774: 'jigs byed chen po r+aa hu la //
NK037(ji)001:775: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu //
NK037(ji)001:776: mgo lus med par mig gis gang //
NK037(ji)001:777: ro stod srin po ro smad sbrul //
NK037(ji)001:778: 'jigs pa'i sku mdog dud kha la //
NK037(ji)001:779: g.yas pa gri gug dgra srog gcod //
NK037(ji)001:780: g.yon gyi zhags pas bla srog 'ching //
NK037(ji)001:781: nyi ma zla ba lto ru za //
NK037(ji)001:782: nyi ma'i rjes gcod shar du rgyu //
NK037(ji)001:783: zla ba'i rjes gcod nub tu rgyu //
NK037(ji)001:784: nyin mo rgyu bas bla srog sdud //
NK037(ji)001:785: mtshan mo rgyu zhing srog dbugs gcod //
NK037(ji)001:786: gza' gdong srin po'i dmag tshogs 'gyed //
NK037(ji)001:787: dmag dpon chen po khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)001:788: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:790: byang shar khrag mtsho mer ba'i nang //
NK037(ji)001:791: dug rlangs 'khyil ba'i bse mkhar na //
NK037(ji)001:792: ma gcig gnyan gyi re ma ti //
NK037(ji)001:793: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa la //
NK037(ji)001:794: khrag gi ral pa mun ltar gtibs //
NK037(ji)001:795: spyi bo'i gtsug na zla bas brgyan //
NK037(ji)001:796: lte ba'i dbus nas nyi ma 'char //
NK037(ji)001:797: srid pa'i bla rku tshe srog 'phrog /
NK037(ji)001:798: snyan cha seng sbrul dril bus brgyan //
NK037(ji)001:799: thams cad zil gnon gdug pa 'dul //
NK037(ji)001:800: sku stod zhing gi g.yang gzhi la //
NK037(ji)001:801: rus phreng khrag dang zhag gis brgyan //
NK037(ji)001:802: sku smad re lde'i sham thabs la //
NK037(ji)001:803: sbrul dang thod rlon dril bu brgyan //
NK037(ji)001:804: chibs su drel rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK037(ji)001:805: g.yas na gshin rje'i khram bam 'phyar //
NK037(ji)001:806: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa rnams //
NK037(ji)001:807: btsan gyi shwa rdel phyogs bcur 'phen //
NK037(ji)001:808: nad kyi rkyal pa dgra la rdeb //
NK037(ji)001:810: 'dod khams bdag mo khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)001:811: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:812: gzhan yang mgon po'i bka' 'khor na //
NK037(ji)001:813: blon po dmag dpon sde dpon dang //
NK037(ji)001:814: ru 'dren pho nya mngag par bcas //
NK037(ji)001:815: ci bgyi bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)001:816: sprul pa yang sprul 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)001:817: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)001:818: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:819: ces sogs kyis rgya cher bstod cing /
NK037(ji)001:822: rnam dag dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK037(ji)001:823: thugs rjes khros pa'i skur bstan nas //
NK037(ji)001:824: bdud dpung 'joms pa'i las mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)001:825: legs ldan mgon la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)001:826: bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba yi //
NK037(ji)001:827: dur khrod chen po'i klong dkyil na //
NK037(ji)001:828: mi mthun phyogs su gyur pa kun //
NK037(ji)001:829: sgrol mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)001:830: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK037(ji)001:831: bstan pa phyogs bcur skyong mdzad cing //
NK037(ji)001:832: gnod byed thams cad pham mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)001:833: mthu chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)001:834: ces pa tsam gyis bstod pa'i mthar 'khor bstod rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa sbyar bar bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:835: bcu gcig pa bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:836: mgon po'i thugs kar dwangs ma'i srog yig h'u mthing
NK037(ji)001:837: nag gi mtha' bskor du bzla bya'i sngags kyi phreng
NK037(ji)001:838: ba me stag gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro bas g.yas su
NK037(ji)001:839: bskor bar gyur / bdag dpal chen por gsal ba'i
NK037(ji)001:840: thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer sna tshogs lcags
NK037(ji)001:842: mgon po'i thugs ka'i h'u yig nas bzung bas rang
NK037(ji)001:843: dbang med par dbang du bsdu pas ci bgyi'i bka'
NK037(ji)001:844: nod cing phrin las rab 'byams thogs med du sgrub
NK037(ji)001:845: par bsam zhing / bzla bya'i sngags ni /
NK037(ji)001:846: b+hurkura ma h+aa pad+ma rde burtsi bur byi ge byi
NK037(ji)001:847: ma na se e ho sho mo kro d+ha h+aum
NK037(ji)001:850: b+hu ru kurma a pra rna bud tsi ke bi
NK037(ji)001:851: ma na se kha sho mo ba kro d+ha h+aum
NK037(ji)001:854: b+hu ru ku ru i tsi ki byi u tsush+ma kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK037(ji)001:855: ces sgrub pa'i gsang sngags so //
NK037(ji)001:857: ces sgrub pa chen po'i sngags so //
NK037(ji)001:859: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis mgon po'i thugs rgyud bskul bas /
NK037(ji)001:860: de'i thugs ka nas 'od zer me'i phreng ba lta
NK037(ji)001:861: bus 'khor rnams bskul bas ci bcol ba'i las mdzad
NK037(ji)001:862: par bsam la / badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya h+aum /
NK037(ji)001:863: badz+ra yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya h+aum /
NK037(ji)001:864: badz+ra rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya h+aum /
NK037(ji)001:865: badz+ra tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK037(ji)001:867: de ltar rim pa bzhin stong ngam brgya brgya'i tshigs
NK037(ji)001:868: su mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang khyad par bdud
NK037(ji)001:871: drag po'i sku lnga rgyal po'i bka' sdod mchog /
NK037(ji)001:872: ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK037(ji)001:873: phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK037(ji)001:874: legs ldan 'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)001:875: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:876: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas dgyes par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:877: dam tshig 'gal 'khrul nyams chag mthol zhing bshags //
NK037(ji)001:878: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)001:879: ces bstod cing phrin las kyang gsol lo //
NK037(ji)001:880: bcu gnyis pa tshogs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:881: bdag bskyed gang la brten pa de'i gzhung bzhin sbyar bas khyab cing /
NK037(ji)001:882: dmigs gsal 'di nyid la sbyar bar spro na /
NK037(ji)001:883: tshogs rdzas rnams bdud rtsi ltar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK037(ji)001:884: tshogs phud cha gsum du spros te /
NK037(ji)001:887: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:889: ga na tsakra p+au dza kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:893: de'i tshul brjod pa la gsum las /
NK037(ji)001:894: dang po bskang rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:896: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las gnas khang dur khrod
NK037(ji)001:897: drag po'i zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab par phyi
NK037(ji)001:898: nang gsang ba'i mchod pa spyan gzigs mthun rdzas rten
NK037(ji)001:899: rdzas bskang rdzas la sogs pa thams cad srid zhi'i
NK037(ji)001:900: 'dod yon gyi rnam pa mkho dgu tshang ba bzang
NK037(ji)001:901: dgus 'byor pa mdzes dgus brgyan pa ngo bo ye
NK037(ji)001:902: shes sgyu ma'i rang bzhin bde ba'i rnam pa thams
NK037(ji)001:903: cad par 'char bas nam mkha'i khams thams cad gang
NK037(ji)001:904: bar bsam la / nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya'am /
NK037(ji)001:905: rgyas par sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin brlab bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:906: gnyis pa thugs dam bskang ba dngos ni /
NK037(ji)001:908: bdag ni rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK037(ji)001:909: dam la gnas shing lha la 'phreng //
NK037(ji)001:910: khyod ni srung ma mthu rtsal can //
NK037(ji)001:911: sngon tshe dpal chen spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)001:912: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:913: khyed kyi dam bca' gnyan po de //
NK037(ji)001:914: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bskul na //
NK037(ji)001:915: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:916: ma h+aa k+aa la gnas 'dir byon //
NK037(ji)001:917: legs ldan nag po dur khrod sgrol ging rdo rje
NK037(ji)001:918: sgrol byed sa bcu'i dbang phyug rig 'dzin srung ma
NK037(ji)001:919: rnal 'byor dgra lha tshogs bdag chen po gnas 'dir
NK037(ji)001:920: byon // bos so chos skyong snyan ma sra //
NK037(ji)001:921: g.yab bo legs ldan spyan ma rtul //
NK037(ji)001:922: bsgrub bo tshogs bdag dgongs ma g.yel //
NK037(ji)001:923: bskul lo bdud rgyal mthu ma chung //
NK037(ji)001:924: do nub khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:925: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:927: me tog spos dang mar me dri //
NK037(ji)001:928: zhal zas rol mo'i bye brag dang //
NK037(ji)001:929: 'phan gdugs lhab lhub sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)001:930: legs ldan 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:931: sha chen lnga ni ri ltar spungs //
NK037(ji)001:932: bdud rtsi lnga ni mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK037(ji)001:933: ye shes lnga ldan dam rdzas 'dis //
NK037(ji)001:934: dpal mgon 'khor bcas sha chen khrag dang dbang po lnga //
NK037(ji)001:935: tshil chen zhun mar mkhris pa dang //
NK037(ji)001:936: g.yang gzhi lhab lhub rkang gling sgras //
NK037(ji)001:937: dpal mgon 'khor bcas dmar chen bza' baca'i gtor ma dang //
NK037(ji)001:938: 'bru bcud bdud rtsi'i btung ba'i rgyun //
NK037(ji)001:939: khyad par dam rdzas sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)001:940: dpal mgon gling bzhi gling phran ri rab dang //
NK037(ji)001:941: rin chen bdun dang bkra shis rdzas //
NK037(ji)001:942: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa yis //
NK037(ji)001:943: dpal mgon g.yag nag rta nag khyi nag dang //
NK037(ji)001:944: lug nag bya nag la sogs pa //
NK037(ji)001:945: rten pa'i dam rdzas sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)001:946: dpal mgon 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:948: dpal ldan ma h+aa k+aa la dang //
NK037(ji)001:951: rtag gtor chen pos thugs phrin las gnyan po bskul ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:952: rgyun gtor nar mas dam tshig gnyan po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:953: bdud rtsi sman gyis rak+ta skom du 'thung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:954: dmar chen ar+g+hasa longs spyod dmar la byed pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:955: sha khrag bshos bus tha mal snang zhen sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:956: bskyed rim gsal bas thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:957: bzlas brjod sngags kyis mchog gi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:958: ting 'dzin mchog gis thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:959: dam tshig nyams chag bskang ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:960: gdung sems dad pas 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:961: g.yab dar nag pos sgrub mchog bu bzhin skyong ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:962: mthing nag ber gyis dam nyams dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:963: phyag mtshan mtshon chas rnal 'byor srung skyob mgon mdzad phyir //
NK037(ji)001:964: sra brtan go yis mthun pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:965: dam rdzas rten bzhis gsang ba'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:966: gri rgod snying gis thugs dam gnyan po bskang ba yis //
NK037(ji)001:967: tshogs bdag 'khor bcas mnyes gyur cig /
NK037(ji)001:969: dgongs shig mgon po thod phreng rtsal //
NK037(ji)001:970: rgyal ba'i bka' la mi nyan med //
NK037(ji)001:971: zab mo'i don la mi sems med //
NK037(ji)001:972: mna' dang khrims la mi brten med //
NK037(ji)001:973: zas dang skom la mi chags med //
NK037(ji)001:974: do nub khyod kyi thugs dam do nub nyams chag ma lus bskang //
NK037(ji)001:975: do nub zhig ral ma lus gso //
NK037(ji)001:976: do nub lha la bshags pa byed //
NK037(ji)001:977: do nub lha la sems 'khon sbyong //
NK037(ji)001:978: do nub nyes par khas kyang len //
NK037(ji)001:979: do nub mnyes pa'i zas shig 'dren //
NK037(ji)001:980: do nub mdza' ba'i gzhung zhig srong //
NK037(ji)001:981: do nub byams pa'i lan cig ldon //
NK037(ji)001:982: do nub snga ma'i gtang rag gtong //
NK037(ji)001:983: do nub phyi ma'i zhu skyems 'bul //
NK037(ji)001:984: do nub khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:985: ma h+aa k+aa la'i thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)001:986: legs ldan nag po'i tshogs bdag chen po'i dur khrod
NK037(ji)001:987: bdag po'i sgrol ging chen po'i kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai'i
NK037(ji)001:988: las mgon nag po'i kro d+ha khro bo'i yak+sha gnod
NK037(ji)001:989: sbyin rak+sha srin po'i 'dod khams bdag mo'i dur khrod
NK037(ji)001:990: ma tshogs 'khor tshogs rgya mtsho'i pho nya phyag brnyan
NK037(ji)001:991: yang sprul 'bum sde'i thugs dam bskang bskang ngo bshags
NK037(ji)001:993: dam can thugs dam bskangs gyur nas //
NK037(ji)001:994: bdag gi nyams chag byang bar mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:995: dngos grub sgrub la bar gcod pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:996: 'gal rkyen bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK037(ji)001:997: mthun rkyen bsam pa thams cad sgrubs //
NK037(ji)001:998: rtag tu thugs dam ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)001:999: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1001: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:1002: hoh yon tan lhun rdzogs dngos grub stsol mdzad pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:1003: rtsa brgyud bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor lha //
NK037(ji)001:1004: dpal chen rdo rje srin po khro bo'i rgyal //
NK037(ji)001:1005: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)001:1006: theg chen gsang sngags bla med sgor zhugs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1007: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1008: rtag tu bsrung zhing sdom par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1009: nyams chag 'gal 'khrul nongs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)001:1010: thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor sgom par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1011: tha mal las la yengs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)001:1012: bde gshegs thugs rgyud bskul bar khas blas nas //
NK037(ji)001:1013: don med long gtam smras pa dmigs med ye shes
NK037(ji)001:1014: sgom par dug gsum rtog pa'i dbang gyur phyi nang
NK037(ji)001:1015: gsang rten 'dzugs par dgos pa'i dam rdzas ma tshang
NK037(ji)001:1016: rtag tu mchod bstod bsnyen par snyoms las le los
NK037(ji)001:1017: yengs pa man ngag sbas nas sgrub par gsang ba'i
NK037(ji)001:1018: gnyen ka 'chol ba dam rdzas phud kyis mchod par
NK037(ji)001:1019: 'bags btsog nyams par gyur pa rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin
NK037(ji)001:1020: sgrub par gzu lum ras chod bgyis pa zol med
NK037(ji)001:1021: dam tshig srung bar khams blangs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1022: nyams grib skyon gyis phog pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)001:1023: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gi //
NK037(ji)001:1024: dam tshig 'gal ba ma lus so sor bshags //
NK037(ji)001:1025: mthol bshags 'bul lo tshangs par mdzad nas kyang //
NK037(ji)001:1026: dngos grub mchog gis bdag rgyud gtams par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1027: ces dang yi ge brgya pa mang du bazla'o //
NK037(ji)001:1028: de nas mdos kyi bskang ba byed par spro na skabs 'dir bya ste logs su blta'o //
NK037(ji)001:1029: gsum pa tshogs tha ma dang 'brel ba'i drag po'i phrin las spyi tsam du sgrub pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:1030: tshogs zan dmigs bya'i gzugs su bcas pa'am mos te /
NK037(ji)001:1031: rang gi snying ga nas spros pa'i pho nya rnams
NK037(ji)001:1032: kyi gnod byed dgra bgegs thams cad bkug nas bstim
NK037(ji)001:1033: par bsam zhing / bden pa'i stobs brjod de dgug
NK037(ji)001:1034: gzhug byas la drag sngags kyi mthar gnod byed +aa
NK037(ji)001:1035: kar+sha ya dzahdzah dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes dgug gzhug bya
NK037(ji)001:1036: par bsam zhing / / mtshon chas gdab cing /
NK037(ji)001:1038: dur khrod sgrol ging tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:1039: legs ldan nag po ma rungs pa //
NK037(ji)001:1040: rgyal ba'i bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:1041: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1042: m+aa ra ya yi las bcol gyis //
NK037(ji)001:1043: tshe srog hur thum myur du sgrol //
NK037(ji)001:1044: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig can //
NK037(ji)001:1045: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK037(ji)001:1046: zhe sdang dregs pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1047: sems can gdug pa'i srog phrogs la //
NK037(ji)001:1048: sha la zo zhing khrag la 'thung //
NK037(ji)001:1049: dam nyams dgra bo myur du sgrol //
NK037(ji)001:1050: m+aa ra ya yi dus la bab //
NK037(ji)001:1051: gzhi snying bsgril ba'i sngags mthar /
NK037(ji)001:1052: sarba sh+aa t+r+aum m+aa ra ya rbad /
NK037(ji)001:1053: ces ling+ga dum bur gtubs pa'i sha khrag bdud rtsir spel ba zhal du stob cing /
NK037(ji)001:1054: hoh dus gsum bde gshegs rgyal ba'i zhal du kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:1055: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po'i dpa' mgon legs ldan
NK037(ji)001:1056: nag po'i yum chen khro mo'i dbang phyug bka' sdod
NK037(ji)001:1057: dregs pa rnam bzhi'i pho nya 'khor tshogs rgya mtsho'i
NK037(ji)001:1058: dug gsum sha khrag mchod par bzhes shig kha ram
NK037(ji)001:1059: kh+aa hi / bzhes shig rol gcig dgyes par rol cig kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:1060: ma h+aa m+aam sa rak+ta kem ni ri ti a mri ta p+au dza kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)001:1061: zhes stob pa byas nas tshogs la rol zhing lhag ma bsngo ba sogs spyi ltar ro //
NK037(ji)001:1062: bcu gsum pa drag po'i las la ched du bskul ba la gnyis las /
NK037(ji)001:1063: dang po drag sngags bzla ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:1064: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer me'i phung po lta bu 'phros /
NK037(ji)001:1065: mgon po'i thugs rgyud bskul bas de nyid khros 'khrugs rngams pas 'khor rnams bskul /
NK037(ji)001:1066: de rnams kyis kyang sprul pa'i pho nya mtshon cha
NK037(ji)001:1067: can dpag med bu yug 'tshub pa ltar spros pas
NK037(ji)001:1068: dgra bgegs thams cad bsad bcad zos bar bsam zhing
NK037(ji)001:1069: sngar gyi sngags rnams cung zad bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK037(ji)001:1070: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la n+ri thum lam thum
NK037(ji)001:1071: ril rbad bu n+ri dzah dgra bo'i snying la ya
NK037(ji)001:1072: / trag rak+sha m+aa ra ya thum ril rbad /
NK037(ji)001:1073: dgra bo'i snying ga gar ga ni dzahb+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK037(ji)001:1074: zhes brgya rtsa sogs ci nus drag tu bazla'o //
NK037(ji)001:1075: gnyis pa bskul ba dngos ni /
NK037(ji)001:1076: sman rag gi phud kyis mchod cing /
NK037(ji)001:1078: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:1079: bar snang khams na bzhugs tsa na //
NK037(ji)001:1080: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK037(ji)001:1081: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ni //
NK037(ji)001:1082: dbang bskur ming btags mnga' gsol ba //
NK037(ji)001:1083: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:1084: tshogs bdag rdo rje thod phreng can //
NK037(ji)001:1085: bdag gis bsnyen cing bos pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)001:1086: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)001:1087: phrin las snyan snyun gsol ba ni //
NK037(ji)001:1088: lha yi dgra lhar mnga' gsol bas //
NK037(ji)001:1089: lha min 'dul ba'i mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:1090: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK037(ji)001:1091: sku la mtshon khrab nag po gsol //
NK037(ji)001:1092: g.yas pa gsal shing dgra la 'phyar //
NK037(ji)001:1093: g.yon pa shun gyi mdung ring bsnams //
NK037(ji)001:1094: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs thog ser 'bebs //
NK037(ji)001:1095: tshur spyod drag po'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1097: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK037(ji)001:1098: 'gro ba'i don du ma la yar //
NK037(ji)001:1099: ko ka thang dmar lad+ga'i yul //
NK037(ji)001:1100: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo ru //
NK037(ji)001:1101: bdud rgyal nag po btul nas ni //
NK037(ji)001:1103: dbang bskur ming btags dam tshig phog /
NK037(ji)001:1104: chos skyong srung mar dam bcas nas //
NK037(ji)001:1105: rigs des rgyal ba'i sras su byas //
NK037(ji)001:1106: de tshe khyod kyis khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1107: rnal 'byor yongs kyi grogs bya zhing //
NK037(ji)001:1108: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK037(ji)001:1109: bkur zhing dgos pa kun sgrub pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:1110: dam las ma 'da' phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1111: bstan pa bsrung ba'i mgon gyur pas //
NK037(ji)001:1112: de phyir mgon po nag por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1113: khyod ni sde brgyad kun gyi rje //
NK037(ji)001:1114: de phyir lang+ka'i bdag por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1115: khyod ni lha srin tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:1116: de phyir tshogs bdag chen por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1117: khyod ni dam chos sgrub pa'i grogs //
NK037(ji)001:1118: de phyir legs ldan nag por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1119: khyod ni ma mo kun gyi gtso //
NK037(ji)001:1120: de phyir dur khrod bdag por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1121: dam nyams rnams kyi gshed ma mdzad //
NK037(ji)001:1122: de phyir sgrol ging chen por grags //
NK037(ji)001:1123: mtshan drug nas ni bskul lags na //
NK037(ji)001:1124: gru gsum mthing nag lcags mkhar nas //
NK037(ji)001:1126: dmar gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)001:1127: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1128: dus ngan gdul daka'i sems can rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1129: ma thogs myur du bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)001:1130: rnal 'byor chen po yongs bstod cing //
NK037(ji)001:1131: khyod la mthun pa'i rdzas 'bul gyis //
NK037(ji)001:1132: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK037(ji)001:1133: khas blangs dam bca' mna' bor ba'i //
NK037(ji)001:1134: dam baca'i mtha' tshig ma 'da' zhig /
NK037(ji)001:1135: sngon yang rig 'dzin gong mas bsgrubs //
NK037(ji)001:1136: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bskul na //
NK037(ji)001:1137: bam ril thod pa'i mkhar rtse nas //
NK037(ji)001:1138: sgrol ging chen po sku bskyed cig /
NK037(ji)001:1139: ru mtshon nag po bu ru ru //
NK037(ji)001:1140: mtshon cha sna tshogs char du 'bebs //
NK037(ji)001:1141: bdud mda' nag po zangs se zang //
NK037(ji)001:1142: bdud bya nag po lding zhing 'dzum //
NK037(ji)001:1143: sna tshogs dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK037(ji)001:1144: mche gtsigs rngams pa'i zhal gdangs nas //
NK037(ji)001:1145: nyams pa'i snying khrag zhal du gsol //
NK037(ji)001:1146: lha chen khyod kyi bka' 'khor na //
NK037(ji)001:1147: sprul pa'i khro bo khro mo 'khrigs //
NK037(ji)001:1148: srin po srin mo rkan sgra sdeb //
NK037(ji)001:1149: gnod sbyin pho mo'i dmag dpung bzlog /
NK037(ji)001:1150: za byed pho mo sha khrag rol //
NK037(ji)001:1152: so so'i bzhugs gnas tha dad pa'i //
NK037(ji)001:1153: yid bzhin nor bu'i thugs dam ni //
NK037(ji)001:1154: yongs su rdzogs pa sgrub par byos //
NK037(ji)001:1155: tshogs bdag chen po 'khor bcas kyi //
NK037(ji)001:1156: thugs dam gnyan po'i dus la bab //
NK037(ji)001:1157: ces bskul zhing phrin las gsol lo //
NK037(ji)001:1158: thun mong ma yin pa'i las sbyor sgrub par 'dod na de'i man ngag ni gzhan du blta'o //
NK037(ji)001:1159: bcu bzhi pa gtor ma stob pa ni /
NK037(ji)001:1160: rgyun gyi phrin las la thun gtor nyid dang gzhan
NK037(ji)001:1161: du bskang gso'i gtor ma gang bshams gtong ba ste
NK037(ji)001:1162: / rak+ta bran la dmigs bya dgug /
NK037(ji)001:1163: sman phud bran nas bdud rtsir spel /
NK037(ji)001:1166: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:1167: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)001:1168: nye gnas kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma //
NK037(ji)001:1169: ging dang gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK037(ji)001:1170: ma mo mkha' 'gro pho nya dang //
NK037(ji)001:1171: sprul pa yang sprul 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)001:1172: zag med 'dod yon bdud rtsi yi //
NK037(ji)001:1173: dam rdzas mchod gtor 'di bzhes la /
NK037(ji)001:1174: deng 'dir bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1175: sngar bcol las kyi gtang rag mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1176: phyi bcol las kyi gsos su bzhes //
NK037(ji)001:1177: sangs rgyas bstan pa khyod kyis srungs //
NK037(ji)001:1178: dkon mchog dbu 'phang khyod kyis bstod //
NK037(ji)001:1179: slob dpon sku dgra khyod kyis thul //
NK037(ji)001:1180: sgrub pa po yi stong grogs mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1181: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)001:1182: ces gtor ma sgrub khang gi yang thog sogs gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK037(ji)001:1183: bco lnga pa mchod cing gsol ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:1184: slar yang ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar gyis phyi mchod dang smad raka gtor mas mchod /
NK037(ji)001:1185: bstod thung gis bstod la phrin las smon lam du gsol ba ni /
NK037(ji)001:1186: hoh mgon po khyod mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK037(ji)001:1187: phyogs dang dus ni thams cad du //
NK037(ji)001:1188: sems can legs don 'byor ba la //
NK037(ji)001:1189: gegs kyi rnam pa kun med shog /
NK037(ji)001:1190: rta dang glang po nor dang 'bru //
NK037(ji)001:1191: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1192: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK037(ji)001:1193: thams cad 'byor ba ldan par shog /
NK037(ji)001:1194: 'gro ba nyes med bde gyur nas //
NK037(ji)001:1195: nad dang mu ge kun bral shog /
NK037(ji)001:1196: rgyal po dge zhing des pa rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1197: chos kyi rgyal srid skyong bar shog /
NK037(ji)001:1198: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa ni //
NK037(ji)001:1199: phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa dang //
NK037(ji)001:1200: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK037(ji)001:1201: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK037(ji)001:1202: dge ba thams cad yongs bsngo zhing //
NK037(ji)001:1203: mgon po khyod mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK037(ji)001:1204: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1205: longs spyod rnam gnyis rdzogs pa dang //
NK037(ji)001:1206: bdag cag byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK037(ji)001:1208: ces smon lam du gsol lo //
NK037(ji)001:1209: bcu drug pa nongs bshags ni /
NK037(ji)001:1210: yi ge brgya pa ci nus su bzla zhing /
NK037(ji)001:1211: ma rnyed yongs su ma tshang dang //
NK037(ji)001:1212: zhes sogs kyis bzod par gsol lo //
NK037(ji)001:1213: bcu bdun pa rjes bsdu ni /
NK037(ji)001:1214: rten yod na brtan bzhugs dang /
NK037(ji)001:1215: med na badz+ra muhs ye shes pa gshegs /
NK037(ji)001:1216: dam tshig pa rang nyid la bstim /
NK037(ji)001:1218: mgrin +aah snying gar h+aum yig gis mtshan par gyur /
NK037(ji)001:1219: badz+ra rak+sha ham gis bdag bsrung /
NK037(ji)001:1220: slar yang smon lam dang bkra shis ci rigs pa bya'o //
NK037(ji)001:1221: sangs rgyas kun dngos dpal chen he ru ka /
NK037(ji)001:1222: rang gi bstan pa bsrung phyir phrin las bzhis //
NK037(ji)001:1223: rnam rol legs ldan nag po tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)001:1224: mchod pa'i phrin las mdo tsam brjod pa ste //
NK037(ji)001:1225: rgyud lung rtsa ba'i gnad rnams ma 'chugs shing //
NK037(ji)001:1226: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes man ngag rnams //
NK037(ji)001:1227: tshang zhing gsal bar brjod las phrin las bzhi //
NK037(ji)001:1228: lhun grub he ru ka dpal myur thob shog /
NK037(ji)001:1229: dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs
NK037(ji)001:1230: phrin las kyi cho ga las bzhi'i rnam rol zhes
NK037(ji)001:1231: bya ba / gang las ston pa rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK037(ji)001:1232: lung dang khyad par gyi sgos rgyud man ngag gi
NK037(ji)001:1234: bde bshegs zur chung gis mdzad pa'i cho ga'i khrigs
NK037(ji)001:1235: la gzhi byas nas byin rlabs kyi tshan kha mi
NK037(ji)001:1236: nyams pa'i phyir yig rnying khungs ma kho na khrigs
NK037(ji)001:1237: bsdebs bklags chog gi tshul du rig pa 'dzin pa
NK037(ji)001:1238: 'gyur med rdo rjes o rgyan smin grol gling gi
